	<h1 class="mb-4">Awards and Recognition</h1>

	<ul class="awards">
		<li>Yuri came in&nbsp;at&nbsp;number 52&nbsp;on Forbes&rsquo; <a href="https://www.forbes.com/midas/#71729ed25650" target="_blank">2018 Midas List</a> of&nbsp;the best dealmakers in&nbsp;hi-tech and life sciences venture capital.</li>
		<li>In&nbsp;2017 Forbes celebrated its centenary by&nbsp;publishing 100 Greatest Living Business Minds&nbsp;&ndash; &ldquo;an&nbsp;A-to-Z encyclopedia of&nbsp;ideas from 100&nbsp;entrepreneurs, visionaries and prophets of&nbsp;capitalism.&rdquo; In&nbsp;his <a href="https://www.forbes.com/100-greatest-business-minds/person/yuri-milner" target="_blank">contribution</a>, Yuri described the long-term perspective&nbsp;&ndash; &ldquo;looking beyond the horizon&rdquo;&nbsp;&ndash; that drew him to&nbsp;America and inspired his science and technology investments.</li>
		<li>In&nbsp;March 2017 Yuri <a href="http://fortune.com/worlds-greatest-leaders/yuri-milner-40/" target="_blank">appeared</a> in&nbsp;Fortune&rsquo;s collection of&nbsp;The World&rsquo;s 50&nbsp;Greatest Leaders.</li>
		<li>In&nbsp;April 2017 Yuri <a href="https://www.forbes.com/pictures/fhgl45lhmj/15-yuri-milner/#7bd1b3299667" target="_blank">came in&nbsp;at&nbsp;number 15</a>&nbsp;in&nbsp;Forbes&rsquo; Midas List of&nbsp;&ldquo;the 100 best venture capitalists in&nbsp;the world,&rdquo; citing his tech investments and Breakthrough Listen initiative.</li>
		<li>In&nbsp;August 2016 Wired placed Yuri at&nbsp;number 20&nbsp;in&nbsp;its <a href="https://www.wired.co.uk/article/wired-global-100" target="_blank">Wired 100</a> list of&nbsp;&ldquo;key influencers... who are shaping our culture, the tech economy, consumer behaviour, scientific discovery&nbsp;&ndash; in&nbsp;short, the people making things happen,&rdquo; noting his investment history and the Breakthrough Starshot interstellar mission he&nbsp;launched earlier that year.</li>
		<li>In&nbsp;August 2016 Forbes included Yuri at&nbsp;number 72&nbsp;in&nbsp;<a href="https://www.forbes.com/richest-in-tech/#6428893c7316" target="_blank">The 100 Richest Tech Billionaires In&nbsp;The World In&nbsp;2016</a>.</li>
		<li>Stephen Hawking wrote <a href="http://time.com/4300003/yuri-milner-2016-time-100/" target="_blank">Yuri&rsquo;s entry</a> in&nbsp;the 2016 edition of&nbsp;TIME&rsquo;s iconic TIME 100 list of&nbsp;the world&rsquo;s most influential people. The cosmologist called him a&nbsp;&ldquo;visionary&rdquo; whose &ldquo;investments take the long view,&rdquo; based on&nbsp;a&nbsp;deep respect for the Universe and humanity.</li>
		<li>Yuri appeared at&nbsp;number 17&nbsp;in&nbsp;the 2016 Forbes Midas List.</li>
		<li>In&nbsp;April 2016 Yuri <a href="https://www.forbes.com/pictures/hejl45fe/yuri-milner/#561859d18b46" target="_blank">appeared</a> in&nbsp;the &ldquo;The Midas China List&rdquo; of&nbsp;prominent investors in&nbsp;Chinese hi-tech companies.</li>
		<li>In&nbsp;September 2015 Yuri placed at&nbsp;23&nbsp;in&nbsp;Vanity Fair&rsquo;s famous <a href="https://www.vanityfair.com/news/photos/2015/09/new-establishment-list-2015" target="_blank">New Establishment</a> List of&nbsp;leaders in&nbsp;technology, media, business, entertainment, politics, and the arts.</li>
		<li><a href="https://www.wired.co.uk/article/the-2015-wired-100" target="_blank">Wired 100</a> included Yuri at&nbsp;number 13&nbsp;in&nbsp;its list of&nbsp;influencers with &ldquo;that special ability to&nbsp;touch the culture, to&nbsp;build scalable success, to&nbsp;connect millions of&nbsp;people.&rdquo;</li>
		<li>&ldquo;The Midas List 2014-&rdquo; Forbes, April 2015.</li>
		<li>Yuri was 25th in&nbsp;Vanity Fair&rsquo;s New Establishment List in&nbsp;2014. The magazine <a href="https://www.vanityfair.com/people/yuri-milner#intcid=dt-hot-link" target="_blank">noted</a> the influence of&nbsp;fellow-physicist and human rights activist Andrei Sakharov on&nbsp;Yuri&rsquo;s long-termist outlook on&nbsp;the world.</li>
		<li>Forbes&rsquo; <a href="https://www.forbes.com/pictures/feie45mif/yuri-milner/#5e6fc4061153" target="_blank">Midas List for 2013</a> included Yuri in&nbsp;53rd position.</li>
		<li>In&nbsp;May 2013 Yuri appeared in&nbsp;Foreign Policy&rsquo;s &ldquo;Power Map: the 500 most powerful people on&nbsp;the planet&rdquo;.</li>
		<li>Yuri was one of&nbsp;the <a href="https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2011-09-07/most-influential-50-people-in-global-finance-full-list-bloomberg-markets" target="_blank">&ldquo;Most Influential&nbsp;50&rdquo;</a>, compiled by&nbsp;Bloomberg Markets in&nbsp;September 2012.</li>
		<li>In&nbsp;February 2012 Business Insider&rsquo;s <a href="https://www.businessinsider.com/the-silicon-valley-100-2012-1" target="_blank">&ldquo;Silicon Valley 100&rdquo;</a> list included Yuri at&nbsp;38.</li>
		<li>Hollywood Reporter&rsquo;s list of&nbsp;<a href="https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/lists/hollywood-reporter-digital-50-power-list-280333/item/dave-morgan-digital-power-50-280376" target="_blank">&ldquo;Top&nbsp;50 Digital Power Players&rdquo;</a> included Yuri in&nbsp;January 2012.</li>
		<li>Fortune placed Yuri at&nbsp;number 19&nbsp;in&nbsp;its <a href="http://archive.fortune.com/galleries/2011/fortune/1111/gallery.business_person_year.fortune/19.html" target="_blank">&ldquo;Businessperson of&nbsp;the Year&nbsp;&ndash; Top&nbsp;50&rdquo;</a> list in&nbsp;November 2011.</li>
		<li>Yuri was Russian GQ&rsquo;s <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20111206005836/http://www.gq.ru/talk/moty/3722" target="_blank">&ldquo;Man of&nbsp;the Year&rdquo;</a> in&nbsp;October 2011.</li>
		<li>In&nbsp;2011 Yuri came in&nbsp;23rd place in&nbsp;Vanity Fair&rsquo;s <a href="https://www.vanityfair.com/news/2011/09/the-2011-new-establishment-list--and-the-top-spot-goes-to---" target="_blank">New Establishment List</a>.</li>
		<li>In&nbsp;June 2011 Yuri appeared in&nbsp;the <a href="https://www.kommersant.ru/doc/1663066" target="_blank">&ldquo;Kommersant of&nbsp;the Year&rdquo;</a> list published by&nbsp;the newspaper Kommersant, selected for &ldquo;showing the optimal balance of&nbsp;risk and profitability for the investor and the management company.&rdquo;</li>
		<li>Yuri was number 3&nbsp;in&nbsp;<a href="https://www.fastcompany.com/person/yuri-milner" target="_blank">Fast Company&rsquo;s &ldquo;100 Most Creative People&rdquo;</a> list in&nbsp;May 2011.</li>
		<li>Forbes&rsquo; 2011 <a href="https://www.forbes.com/lists/midas/2011/midas-list-complete-list.html" target="_blank">Midas List of&nbsp;Tech&rsquo;s Top Investors</a> named Yuri 25th in&nbsp;its list.</li>
		<li>Yuri appeared in&nbsp;Forbes&rsquo; list of&nbsp;<a href="https://www.forbes.com/lists/2011/10/billionaires_2011.html" target="_blank">&ldquo;The World&rsquo;s Billionaires 2011&rdquo;</a>.</li>
		<li>Russian Forbes placed Yuri in&nbsp;first position in&nbsp;its <a href="http://www.forbes.ru/tehno-slideshow/internet-i-telekommunikatsii/63930-hozyaeva-virtualnoi-realnosti" target="_blank">&ldquo;Owners of&nbsp;Virtual Reality&rdquo;</a> list in&nbsp;February 2011.</li>
		<li>Yuri was <a href="https://www.vedomosti.ru/newspaper/articles/2010/12/30/biznesmen_goda">&ldquo;Businessman of&nbsp;the Year&rdquo;</a> for 2010 in&nbsp;the business newspaper Vedomosti.</li>
		<li>Yuri was runner-up in&nbsp;Fortune&rsquo;s <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20120118060750/http://money.cnn.com/galleries/2010/technology/1007/gallery.smartest_people_tech.fortune/40.html">&ldquo;Smartest People in&nbsp;Tech&rdquo;</a> list of&nbsp;investors in&nbsp;July 2010.</li>
	</ul>

